The Creative Commons Licensing extension provides the ability to select and embed a Creative Commons license in Writer, Calc, Impress and Draw documents. In addition to embedding the license in the document metadata it provides a visible notice in your document.

In addtion to that this extension supports for adding images from several sources. Users can search images in Flickr, Open Clip Art, Wikimedia Commons and Picasa and add them to documents. The license and attribution data will also be added with the image.